# ===========================================================================
# This repository holds our SWAT+ learning product only:
#   docs/, README.md, AGENTS.md, and workspace config.
# Everything ignored below is an upstream copy, a build artifact, or
# machine-specific state.
# ===========================================================================

# --- Upstream SWAT+ source tree -------------------------------------------
# Tracked as a git submodule (see .gitmodules). Do NOT ignore it.

# --- Visual Studio / Intel Fortran build output and IDE state -------------
/VSProj/**/x64/
/VSProj/**/.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.aps
*.opensdf
*.sdf

# --- Fortran compiler intermediates ---------------------------------------
# Normally produced under x64/; listed here as a safety net.
*.mod
*.obj
*__genmod.f90

# --- CMake build directories ----------------------------------------------
build/

# --- OS / editor cruft ----------------------------------------------------
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~

# --- SWAT+ run outputs inside scenarios -----------------------------------
# Scenario inputs (file.cio, *.bsn, *.lum, *.pcp, ...) stay tracked.
# Uncomment below to also ignore files the model regenerates each run.
# /VSProj/SWAT/Osu_1hru/*.out
# /VSProj/SWAT/Ames_sub1/*.out
# /VSProj/SWAT/*/_aa.txt
# /VSProj/SWAT/*/_yr.txt
